  "title": "M&E Coordinator (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Coordinate M&E installation works and liaise with contractors and consultants.</li><li>Ensure compliance with design drawings, specifications, and safety standards.</li><li>Support troubleshooting of M&E systems and resolve installation challenges.</li><li>Monitor site progress and report issues.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical/Electrical Engineering or equivalent.</li><li>At least 3 years’ experience in M&E works for <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Knowledge of M&E systems, site coordination, and construction standards.</li><li>Ability to interpret M&E drawings and coordinate with multi-disciplinary teams.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
